01:11:04.751 --> 01:11:06.430
you see what I'm saying?
 

01:11:06.430 --> 01:11:12.067
The measure in which evil--if
you get into this metaphysical

01:11:12.067 --> 01:11:17.130
framework,
if there is going to be

01:11:17.130 --> 01:11:23.149
